{"pageProps":{"page":{"slug":"home","title":"Agust Islandia | Gay Music & LGBTQ+ Pop","description":"Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson) is an Icelandic queer pop artist creating gay anthems, LGBTQ+ musicals, full lyrics, and official release pages.","canonical":"/","routePath":"/","language":"en-US","og":{"title":"Agust Islandia | Gay Music & LGBTQ+ Pop","description":"Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson) is an Icelandic queer pop artist creating gay anthems, LGBTQ+ musicals, full lyrics, and official release pages.","image":"/agust_islandia.jpg","type":"profile","url":"/"},"twitter":{"card":"summary_large_image","title":"Agust Islandia | Gay Music & LGBTQ+ Pop","description":"Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson) is an Icelandic queer pop artist creating gay anthems, LGBTQ+ musicals, full lyrics, and official release pages.","image":"/agust_islandia.jpg"},"bodyHtml":"<header class=\"glass-hero\">\n      <div>\n        <span class=\"hero-kicker\">Official Site • Agust Smari Bjarkarson</span>\n        <h1>Agust Islandia<br>LGBTQ+ Pop &amp; Musical Theatre</h1>\n        <p>\n          Agust Islandia is the artist project of <strong>Agust Smari Bjarkarson</strong>, an Icelandic songwriter and producer creating\n          queer pop records and full-length gay musicals. Explore albums, singles, and complete lyric pages centered on\n          queer love, identity, recovery, and chosen family.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n          <a class=\"hero-btn primary\" href=\"/the-unseen-chorus.html\">Listen to The Unseen Chorus</a>\n          <a class=\"hero-btn secondary\" href=\"/swipe-me-to-the-moon.html\">Open Swipe Me to the Moon</a>\n          <a class=\"hero-btn secondary\" href=\"/lyrics.html\">Browse Full Lyrics</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"hero-stat-cloud\" aria-label=\"Key highlights\">\n        <div class=\"stat-pill\"><strong>50+</strong><span>Lyrics pages published</span></div>\n        <div class=\"stat-pill\"><strong>3</strong><span>Full gay musicals</span></div>\n        <div class=\"stat-pill\"><strong>13</strong><span>Release pages live</span></div>\n        <div class=\"stat-pill\"><strong>Worldwide</strong><span>Streaming on Apple &amp; Spotify</span></div>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main id=\"main-content\">\n      <section class=\"glass-grid\">\n        <article class=\"glass-card\">\n          <h2>Three Complete Gay Musicals</h2>\n          <p>75 tracks across three full-length musicals, each one a complete story with a proper ending. Not a playlist. Genuine musical theatre, with all the emotional weight that implies. Start anywhere. The finales are worth it.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"glass-card\">\n          <h2>Full Lyrics for Every Song</h2>\n          <p>50+ complete lyric pages, one for every song. You can't get the full story from streaming alone. Read while you listen, or just sit with something that got to you.</p>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"glass-card\">\n          <h2>Icelandic Gay Pop &amp; Pride Anthems</h2>\n          <p>Agust Islandia is an Icelandic gay songwriter making queer pop records with actual stories in them. Pride anthems and three full gay musicals, all documented here with complete lyrics and streaming links.</p>\n        </article>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"discography-section\" aria-label=\"Gay and Proud featured player\">\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:minmax(320px,1fr);gap:var(--spacing-md);align-items:start;\">\n          <article class=\"release-card\" style=\"padding:0;border:0;background:transparent;box-shadow:none;\">\n            <iframe title=\"Gay and Proud on Apple Music\" src=\"https://embed.music.apple.com/us/album/out-and-proud/1836369950?theme=dark\" loading=\"lazy\" allow=\"autoplay *; encrypted-media *; fullscreen *; clipboard-write\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" style=\"width:100%;height:450px;border:0;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;\"></iframe>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"discography-section\" aria-label=\"Gay anthem highlights\">\n        <div class=\"discography-head\">\n          <h2>Gay Anthem Highlights</h2>\n          <p>Start here for high-energy Pride songs and core LGBTQ+ anthems from Agust Islandia.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mini-links\">\n          <a href=\"/gay-and-proud.html\">Gay anthem lyrics: Gay and Proud</a>\n          <a href=\"/pride-around-the-world.html\">Global Pride anthem: Pride Around the World</a>\n          <a href=\"/pride-on-the-seas.html\">Pride single: Pride on the Seas</a>\n          <a href=\"/pride-month-2025.html\">Pride collection: Pride Month 2025</a>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"album-row\" aria-label=\"Featured works\">\n        <article class=\"album-card\">\n          <img class=\"album-cover\" src=\"/the-unseen-chorus-cover.webp\" alt=\"The Unseen Chorus album artwork\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"album-body\">\n            <h2>The Unseen Chorus</h2>\n            <p>A 27-track gay musical released October 6, 2025, tracing betrayal, compulsion, shame, healing, and recommitment.</p>\n            <div class=\"mini-links\">\n              <a href=\"/the-unseen-chorus.html\">Album Page</a>\n              <a href=\"/just-an-advisory.html\">Track 1</a>\n              <a href=\"/come-out-of-the-dark.html\">Finale</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n\n        <article class=\"album-card\">\n          <img class=\"album-cover\" src=\"/swipe-me-to-the-moon-cover.webp\" alt=\"Swipe Me to the Moon album artwork\" width=\"632\" height=\"632\" loading=\"lazy\">\n          <div class=\"album-body\">\n            <h2>Swipe Me to the Moon</h2>\n            <p>A 22-track musical released July 18, 2025, following queer love from first swipe to commitment, grief, and renewal.</p>\n            <div class=\"mini-links\">\n              <a href=\"/swipe-me-to-the-moon.html\">Album Page</a>\n              <a href=\"/the-awakening.html\">Track 1</a>\n              <a href=\"/the-grindr-carol.html\">Track 3</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"discography-section\" aria-label=\"Full discography\">\n        <div class=\"discography-head\">\n          <h2>Full Discography</h2>\n          <p>Complete release catalog for Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson).</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"discography-list\">\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/the-unseen-chorus.html\"><strong>The Unseen Chorus (A Gay Musical)</strong><span>2025 • Album</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/album/the-unseen-chorus-a-gay-musical/1844179786\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/0hMwFUq63zUjMyYBKvnq9p\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/swipe-me-to-the-moon.html\"><strong>Swipe Me to the Moon (A Gay Musical)</strong><span>2025 • Album</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/swipe-me-to-the-moon-a-gay-musical/1833359480\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></sv