"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/pride-month-2025.html\"><strong>Pride Month 2025</strong><span>2025 • EP</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/pride-month-2025-ep/1827272560\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/2gJsNkTxkF5zJhFiKtjXsk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/bless-this-mess.html\"><strong>Bless This Mess</strong><span>2025 • Single</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/bless-this-mess-single/1831807697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/3R8ebW1HRFJr6BNs80Q10O\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/peach-and-purple.html\"><strong>Peach and Purple</strong><span>2025 • Single</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/peach-and-purple-single/1830614759\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/7wPE5efhLGm4QhBhzt9vOM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/yogurt.html\"><strong>Yogurt</strong><span>2025 • Single</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/yogurt-single/1830482188\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/3hsviubnVHs2IIHHOOEfgd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/cowboys.html\"><strong>Cowboys</strong><span>2025 • EP</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/album/cowboys-ep/1834409818\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/album/2YcVvOmG9Yfm35ZLHKN5RW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n          <article class=\"release-card\"><a class=\"release-main\" href=\"/the-gay-mormon-musical.html\"><strong>The Gay Mormon Musical</strong><span>2025 • Album</span></a><div class=\"release-links\"><a class=\"stream-btn apple\" href=\"https://music.apple.com/us/artist/agust-smari-bjarkarson/1827272561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Listen on Apple Music\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#apple-icon\"></use></svg></a><a class=\"stream-btn spotify\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/artist/3vCWdArvNjajk3eCmfExNG\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" title=\"Listen on Spotify\"><svg class=\"stream-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><use href=\"#spotify-icon\"></use></svg></a></div></article>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      <section class=\"artist-bio-section\" aria-label=\"About Agust Islandia\">\n        <article class=\"artist-bio-card\">\n          <div class=\"artist-bio-content\">\n            <h2>About Agust Islandia</h2>\n            <img class=\"artist-bio-photo-inline\" src=\"/agust_islandia.webp\" alt=\"Portrait of Agust Islandia (Agust Smari Bjarkarson)\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" style=\"width:180px;height:auto;max-width:180px;\">\n            <p><strong>Agust Islandia</strong> is the artist project of <strong>Agust Smari Bjarkarson</strong>, an Icelandic songwriter, producer, and musical storyteller focused on <em>queer pop</em> and <em>LGBTQ+ musical theatre</em>. His catalog is built around emotionally direct lyric writing with theatrical structure, so songs work both as individual tracks and as chapters inside larger narrative arcs.</p>\n            <p>Two flagship works define this era: <strong>Swipe Me to the Moon (A Gay Musical)</strong> and <strong>The Unseen Chorus (A Gay Musical)</strong>. Together, they document contemporary queer life from first digital connection to intimacy, conflict, grief, accountability, and chosen love. The method is story-first: recurring themes, character growth, and lyrical continuity across full albums.</p>\n            <p>Outside the musicals, singles such as <strong>Gay and Proud</strong>, <strong>My Fire (Mi Fuego)</strong>, and <strong>Feel Alive</strong> expand the project into bilingual anthems, dance-forward releases, and public declarations of queer visibility. This website exists as an <strong>official lyrics and discography archive</strong> so listeners, press, and researchers can move from artist biography to release pages to complete lyrics in one place.</p>\n            <p>Agust Islandia’s direction is clear: write songs with emotional truth, publish full lyrical context, and maintain a long-term queer music archive that stays accessible, human, and culturally useful globally.</p>\n          </div>\n        </article>\n      </section>\n    </main>","schemaGraph":{"@context":"https://schema.org","@graph":[{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-person","name":"Agust Smari Bjarkarson","alternateName":"Agust Islandia","additionalName":["Agust Smari Bjarkarson","Agust Islandia"],"birthDate":"1976-08-26","birthPlace":{"@type":"Place","name":"Reykjavik, Iceland"},"identifier":{"@type":"PropertyValue","propertyID":"ISNI","value":"0000000528099919"},"image":"https://www.gusti.com/agust_islandia.jpg","jobTitle":["Singer-songwriter","Composer","Queer Pop Artist"],"description":"Icelandic queer pop artist and musical storyteller creating gay anthems, full lyric pages, and LGBTQ+ musical theatre projects.","nationality":"Icelandic","sameAs":["https://open.spotify.com/artist/3vCWdArvNjajk3eCmfExNG","https://music.apple.com/us/artist/agust-smari-bjarkarson/1827272561","https://www.tiktok.com/@gusticeland","https://musicbrainz.org/artist/fca2294b-5bbb-4711-881a-aa61e90346f5","https://www.discogs.com/artist/16616054-Agust-Smari-Bjarkarson","https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q136089384"],"url":"https://www.gusti.com/","memberOf":{"@id"