025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Musical Theatre","Pop","LGBTQ+"],"description":"A contemporary gay musical following two men from dating app meeting to deep love. 22 songs explore modern queer romance, first dates, relationship milestones, and finding forever love in the digital age.","numTracks":22,"url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/swipe-me-to-the-moon-a-gay-musical/1833359480","https://open.spotify.com/album/48aiyJl8LaWvG7mRheH8Ky"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#album-the-unseen-chorus","name":"The Unseen Chorus, A Gay Musical","albumProductionType":"http://schema.org/StudioAlbum","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/AlbumRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Musical Theatre","Pop","LGBTQ+"],"description":"The Unseen Chorus – A Gay Musical is an unflinching theatrical work that confronts how the gay community has drifted in the age of apps and online porn, where infidelity has become widespread, promiscuity is often celebrated, and desire is fueled by the constant pursuit of the next, seemingly better partner. Through its narrative and music, the production highlights this vicious cycle while urging reflection and change. It serves as both a mirror and a challenge, asking individuals and the community alike to pause, look inward, and reclaim values of love, honesty, and loyalty. Ultimately, the musical dares audiences to rise above the noise and imagine something truer, stronger, and more human.","url":["https://music.apple.com/album/the-unseen-chorus-a-gay-musical/1844179786","https://open.spotify.com/album/0hMwFUq63zUjMyYBKvnq9p"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#single-yogurt","name":"Yogurt","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/SingleRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop"],"description":"An intriguing pop single with playful energy. The exact themes remain delightfully mysterious - let the music speak for itself!","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/yogurt-single/1830482188","https://open.spotify.com/album/3hsviubnVHs2IIHHOOEfgd"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#single-peach-and-purple","name":"Peach and Purple","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/SingleRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop"],"description":"A colorful pop single blending soft and vibrant tones. The peach and purple palette suggests warmth meets mystique in this melodic creation.","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/peach-and-purple-single/1830614759","https://open.spotify.com/album/7wPE5efhLGm4QhBhzt9vOM"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#single-pride-around-the-world","name":"Pride Around the World","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/SingleRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop","LGBTQ+ Pride"],"description":"A global anthem celebrating LGBTQ+ unity and international Pride solidarity. This uplifting single honors diverse queer communities worldwide and the universal power of Pride.","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/pride-around-the-world-single/1834268047","https://open.spotify.com/album/1GMOoz45QL3Yer9Yx1tJYj"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#single-pride-on-the-seas","name":"Pride on the Seas","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/SingleRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop","LGBTQ+ Pride"],"description":"A nautical Pride anthem celebrating LGBTQ+ freedom and adventure on the open waters. This single captures the spirit of Pride sailing the seas with queer joy and liberation.","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/pride-on-the-seas-single/1832629718","https://open.spotify.com/album/0auDUhna6t34Xgx3Q1FlJa"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#single-bless-this-mess","name":"Bless This Mess","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/SingleRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop"],"description":"A heartfelt anthem about embracing life's beautiful chaos and imperfection. This single celebrates finding grace and blessing in the messy, authentic moments of queer life.","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/bless-this-mess-single/1831807697","https://open.spotify.com/album/3R8ebW1HRFJr6BNs80Q10O"]},{"@type":"MusicAlbum","@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#ep-cowboys","name":"Cowboys","albumProductionType":"http://schema.org/StudioAlbum","albumReleaseType":"http://schema.org/EPRelease","datePublished":"2025","byArtist":{"@id":"https://www.gusti.com/#agust-islandia"},"genre":["Pop","LGBTQ+","Comedy"],"description":"A playful, irreverent take on cowboy culture with queer themes and humor. Features 'Y'all Means All' and 'Two Steers in Love' - subverting Western stereotypes with LGBTQ+ inclusivity and cheeky comedy.","url":["https://music.apple.com/us/album/cowboys-ep/1834409818","https://open.spotify.com/album/2YcVvOmG9Yfm35ZLHKN5RW"]}]}}},"__N_SSG":true}